org.microbean.development.annotation

Annotation Type Issue


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={ANNOTATION_TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,FIELD,LOCAL_VARIABLE,METHOD,PACKAGE,PARAMETER,TYPE,TYPE_PARAMETER,TYPE_USE})
public @interface Issue
    Describes an issue that is related to the annotated element.
    Author:
    Laird Nelson

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String createdOn
      Describes when the issue itself was created.
      String description
      A description of the issue.
      String effect
      A description of the effect the issue has on the annotated element.
      String id
      Identifying information about the issue.
      String resolution
      How the issue was resolved.
      String resolvedOn
      When the issue was resolved.
      String severity
      The severity of the issue.
      String status
      A description of the current status of the issue.
      String type
      The kind of issue this is.
      String uri
      Where more information about the issue may be found.
